nodes.text: Hasbro Inc. released an extensive merchandise collection for the 2016 Star Wars saga film Rogue One: A Star Wars Story. The line premiered on September 30th, 2016 as part of the "Go Rogue" event. Packaging for the line includes a portrait of a death trooper. The line also included some characters from sources beyond the film, with packaging that still featured the death trooper's image but simply removed the subtitle "Rogue One" from below the Star Wars logo.
